{"tid":1753681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"場仗未完架，你地休撚息完未？","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:11:56.000Z","uid":190378,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"efbe80fc22027d2bfefcdb06fa73abfed7f54b81","tid":1753681,"uid":190378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"Poly仲有人，仲有好多人等住要救。<br />\n<br />\n坐10年唔係講玩架..<br />\n<br />\n唔好將幾個月發生左既事忘記得一乾二淨先得架？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續上啊！"},{"pid":"0525ab7fdcd3694269511113e7d5b70c7657b3df","tid":1753681,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:04:23.000Z","msg":"休息完了"},{"pid":"215979729ce53577deb8e13672ec4302481ba32a","tid":1753681,"uid":190378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"唔好扮盲睇唔撚到好無？"},{"pid":"389c7a36f77084b928e8bb62ebb5d5388387ff34","tid":1753681,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f52026e67c7f0c76ad56c5d6241155a41333412a","tid":1753681,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏左喇，但我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"323161c6856e33441fec72c58d5b4fe43f4ad09d","tid":1753681,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:17:24.000Z","msg":"有撚休息過 得你休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dc0a0f9aa7016e1e6c1f6bf07b147b4e631797","tid":1753681,"uid":190378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"b7319f7783bfb2d09334d4ff3eed0fa52433cb98","tid":1753681,"uid":85509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"所有泛民區議員或落選泛民議員<br />\n應該馬上立即公開聯署五大訴求<br />\n署名隔離要括住得票數<br />\n公開夾鳩淋病<br />\n<br />\n只要成功 就可以救到所有手足<br />\npoly手足要頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19179ad9c09e47d332bf38340f2956d55978ab45","tid":1753681,"uid":41005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"535e5089f392f15e292813be8961395aff3806f1","tid":1753681,"uid":184968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:09:14.000Z","msg":"絕對唔會忘記手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb46ceeb479fddb31ae66749b9efc18ebc525b54","tid":1753681,"uid":262875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n不解釋"}]}